    {
      "id": "entry-surfaces-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Problem Statement",
      "position": {
        "x": 20,
        "y": -180
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Named Entry Surfaces\n\nBranch expansion exposed a gap: the same `.node` file may be used as a destination graph or as an inline branch source.\n\nThe port decides the interaction mode, but the target graph needs a declared entry surface so expansion starts from the intended place.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
