    {
      "id": "entry-surfaces-port-contract",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Port-Decided Intent",
      "position": {
        "x": -20,
        "y": 140
      },
      "width": 340,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Port-Decided Intent\n\nThe target file does not hard-code whether it is a graph or a fragment.\n\nThe `port` declares the intent:\n- `mode=navigate` -> open as document\n- `mode=expand` -> use as branch source\n\nThat keeps one artifact reusable in multiple contexts.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
