      "width": 340,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## UX Direction\n\nHide the mechanics. The user should see concrete settings like:\n- `Open at`\n- `Expand from`\n\nNormal users should not have to think about manifests, root fragments, or internal node ids.",
