    {
      "id": "entry-surfaces-fallbacks",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Fallback Resolution",
      "position": {
        "x": 380,
        "y": 440
      },
      "width": 360,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Fallback Resolution\n\nIf a graph does not declare an entry surface:\n1. use the requested handle if present\n2. else use the default/root handle\n3. else use the first root node\n4. else use the first visible node\n\nThis keeps existing graphs working while allowing explicit author control.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
