    {
      "id": "entry-surfaces-structural-only",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Structural-Only Expansion",
      "position": {
        "x": 800,
        "y": 260
      },
      "width": 360,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Structural-Only Expansion\n\nDefault `expand` should import structure, not authority:\n- import nodes and edges\n- strip manifest, legend, dictionary\n- block scripts and executable bindings\n- keep imported content marked as projected structure",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
